            "html": "Typical adult hippos move quickly on land and attack stealthily in the water. Though herbivorous, hippos are notoriously aggressive and territorial.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"563\" game-obj=\"Rules\">Recall Knowledge - Animal</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a></u>)</b>: DC 20<br/><b><u><a aonid=\"563\" game-obj=\"Rules\">Unspecific Lore</a></u></b>: DC 18<br/><b><u><a aonid=\"563\" game-obj=\"Rules\">Specific Lore</a></u></b>: DC 15"
        },
        {
            "name": "Hippopotamus",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
                    "name": "Hippo Sweat",
                    "type": "section",
                    "sources": [
                        {
                            "type": "source",
                            "name": "Bestiary 2",
                            "link": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "Bestiary 2 pg. 144",
                                "alt": "Bestiary 2 pg. 144",
                                "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq022yq"
                            },
                            "page": 144,
                            "errata": {
                                "type": "link",
                                "name": "2.0",
                                "alt": "2.0",
                                "game-obj": "Sources",
                                "aonid": 32
                            }
                        }
                    ],
                    "subtype": "sidebar",
                    "sidebar_type": "additional_lore",
                    "sidebar_heading": "Additional Lore",
                    "image": {
                        "type": "image",
                        "name": "Additional Lore",
                        "image": "Sidebar_2_AdditionalLore.png"
                    },
                    "html": "A hippopotamus's sweat is an unusual reddish color that can lend them an even more frightening appearance that evokes the visage of a blood-coated monster. This sweat helps to protect the hippopotamus from becoming overheated, but it also bolsters their resistance to all manner of diseases."
                }
            ],
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Bestiary 2",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Bestiary 2 pg. 144",
                        "alt": "Bestiary 2 pg. 144",
                        "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq022yq"
                    },
                    "page": 144,
                    "errata": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "2.0",
                        "alt": "2.0",
                        "game-obj": "Sources",
                        "aonid": 32
                    }
                }
            ],
            "html": "Hippopotamuses, or hippos for short, are semiaquatic animals that spend most of their time in rivers and lakes, but they also can thrive on land."
        }
    ],
